info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.Account
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class Account
extends Object
implements Serializable
    An Account has to be created for at least one manager or developer. It is identified by a unique email address. The password ensures the identity. Optionally an account may have information about the user in form of her/his first name and last name. It is possible to change the password, the first name or last name at a later point of time. In addition to creating an account another possible request is to get the created account but only with the correct credentials.
